text: An image shared on Facebook purportedly shows an excerpt of a New York Times interview in which former Vice President Joe Biden says he eats the wooden stick in the center of corn dogs.
Joe Biden said he eats the sticks in corn dogs.
Says Joe Biden talked about eating wooden corn dog sticks.
In December 2020, President-elect Joe Biden, or an official social media account for his dogs Champ and Major, posted pictures of the dogs biting and playing with a Donald Trump chew toy.
